0x58982680// SetInteriorPortalRoomTo
void SET_INTERIOR_PORTAL_ROOM_TO(int interiorId, int portalIndex, int roomTo);Parameters:interiorId: The target interior.portalIndex: Interior portal index.roomTo: New value.Examples:Lualocal playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)

if interiorId ~= 0 then
  local portalIndex = 0

  SetInteriorPortalRoomTo(interiorId, portalIndex, 0)
  RefreshInterior(interiorId)
end

// SetInteriorPortalRoomTo
void SET_INTERIOR_PORTAL_ROOM_TO(int interiorId, int portalIndex, int roomTo);

local playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)

if interiorId ~= 0 then
  local portalIndex = 0

  SetInteriorPortalRoomTo(interiorId, portalIndex, 0)
  RefreshInterior(interiorId)
end
